---
title: Simple Beef and Pork Ragu with Spinach and Roasted Sweet Peppers
description: Beef and pork are a traditional duo in Italian cooking. Tonight, this twosome is also paired with sweet roasted peppers and a rich ragu sauce to create a restaurant-worthy plate of pasta.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragu-simple-au-boeuf-et-au-porc-cd63bdbb.jpg
